NOTE namelist file in git repo is not always in sync with code!

Required Input files/variables

real_options.namelist
	This file specifies all other files and options.  
	Necessary netcdf files: 
		Boundary/Initial conditions in e.g. wrf output files
			must contain QVAPOR, QCLOUD, QICE, T, P, PB, U, V, HGT, XLAT, XLONG
		Hi resolution DEM in e.g. high-res wrf input or output file
			must contain HGT, XLAT, XLONG
			

In the old ideal model:
	init_conditions_file="../../test_data/init.nc"
		lat,lon 2D real
		HGT 2D real (terrain height)

		if optionsfile.readz:
			z 3D real (atm level heights)
		else:
			z=hgt+dz*nth_level-dz/2

	boundary_file="../../test_data/boundary.nc"
		lat,lon 2D real
		HGT 2D real (terrain height)
		driving variables: 3D real
			P,U,V,T,QVAPOR,QCLOUD,QICE
	
		if optionsfile.readz:
			z 3D real (atm level heights)
		else:
			z=hgt+dz*nth_level-dz/2

	output_file="../../test_output/ideal"

